{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01YLqfsiE5YGfHXscLNRY4Tp","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All files have been successfully rewritten with Spring Boot equivalents. Let me create a summary of what was changed:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated all 7 application service layer files from Quarkus to Spring Boot. Here's what was changed in each file:\n\n### 1. **DefaultBookingService.java**\n- **Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultBookingService.java`\n- **Changes:**\n  - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Service`\n  - `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` → `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n  - `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n### 2. **DefaultCargoInspectionService.java**\n- **Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultCargoInspectionService.java`\n- **Changes:**\n  - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Service`\n  - `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` → `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n  - `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n### 3. **DefaultHandlingEventService.java**\n- **Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultHandlingEventService.java`\n- **Changes:**\n  - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Service`\n  - `jakarta.transaction.Transactional(rollbackOn = ...)` → `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional(rollbackFor = ...)`\n  - `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n  - Removed verbose comments to match requested format\n\n### 4. **SampleDataGenerator.java**\n- **Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/SampleDataGenerator.java`\n- **Changes:**\n  - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n  - Removed `@Startup` (Quarkus-specific)\n  - `@PostConstruct` → `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class)`\n  - Removed `@UnlessBuildProfile(\"test\")` (Quarkus-specific)\n  - `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n### 5. **InitLoader.java**\n- **Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/InitLoader.java`\n- **Changes:**\n  - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n  - `@Inject` → `@Autowired` (for Logger, HandlingEventFactory, and HandlingEventRepository)\n  - EntityManager uses `@PersistenceContext` (compatible with Spring)\n  - Changed from `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` → `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n\n### 6. **RestConfiguration.java**\n- **Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/RestConfiguration.java`\n- **Changes:**\n  - Removed JAX-RS annotations (`@ApplicationPath`, extends `Application`)\n  - Converted to empty placeholder class with comment explaining Spring Boot handles REST configuration automatically\n\n### 7. **HandlingEventFactory.java**\n- **Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/handling/HandlingEventFactory.java`\n- **Changes:**\n  - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n  - `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n  - `jakarta.transaction.Transactional(rollbackOn = ...)` → `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional(rollbackFor = ...)`\n\n## Key Migration Patterns Applied:\n\n1. **Dependency Injection:** `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n2. **Bean Scoping:** `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Service` or `@Component`\n3. **Transaction Management:** `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` → `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n4. **Transaction Rollback:** `rollbackOn` → `rollbackFor`\n5. **Lifecycle Events:** `@PostConstruct` + `@Startup` → `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class)`\n6. **JAX-RS Configuration:** Removed (handled by Spring Boot auto-configuration)\n\nAll files have been successfully written and are ready for use in your Spring Boot application."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6fabce19-5bc2-4de5-94d2-1fb45743d165","uuid":"02dd6571-68df-4cda-a950-b9a9df6c4f66"}
