{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01FdBcgP4BXiUvhJdpmQ9G2Q","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully rewritten all 13 infrastructure layer files from Quarkus to Spring Boot. Let me provide you with a comprehensive summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nAll 13 infrastructure layer files have been successfully migrated from Quarkus to Spring Boot. Here's a detailed breakdown:\n\n### 1. **LoggerProducer.java** \n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/logging/LoggerProducer.java`\n- **Changes**: Converted from CDI `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Produces` to Spring `@Configuration` with `@Bean` and `@Scope(\"prototype\")`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 2. **CargoUpdated.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/events/cdi/CargoUpdated.java`\n- **Changes**: Replaced CDI `@Qualifier` import with Spring's `@Qualifier`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 3. **JpaCargoRepository.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaCargoRepository.java`\n- **Changes**: \n  - Removed Panache `PanacheRepositoryBase` implementation\n  - Replaced with standard JPA `EntityManager` using `@PersistenceContext`\n  - Converted CDI annotations to Spring (`@Repository`, `@Transactional`, `@Autowired`)\n  - Replaced CDI `Event<Cargo>` with Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 4. **JpaHandlingEventRepository.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaHandlingEventRepository.java`\n- **Changes**: Removed Panache, added standard JPA `EntityManager`, converted to Spring annotations\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 5. **JpaLocationRepository.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaLocationRepository.java`\n- **Changes**: Removed Panache, added standard JPA with `@Transactional(readOnly = true)`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 6. **JpaVoyageRepository.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaVoyageRepository.java`\n- **Changes**: Removed Panache, added standard JPA with `@Transactional(readOnly = true)`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 7. **ExternalRoutingService.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/routing/ExternalRoutingService.java`\n- **Changes**: \n  - Replaced JAX-RS `WebTarget` with Spring `RestTemplate`\n  - Converted `@ConfigProperty` to `@Value`\n  - Replaced CDI annotations with Spring (`@Service`, `@Transactional`, `@Autowired`)\n  - Removed `@PostConstruct` initialization (RestTemplate is now directly instantiated)\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 8. **JmsApplicationEvents.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/JmsApplicationEvents.java`\n- **Changes**: \n  - Replaced manual JMS `ConnectionFactory` and `JMSContext` management with Spring `JmsTemplate`\n  - Converted to `@Service` with `@Autowired` and `@Value` annotations\n  - Simplified message sending using `jmsTemplate.convertAndSend()`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 9. **CargoHandledConsumer.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/CargoHandledConsumer.java`\n- **Changes**: \n  - Removed Quarkus lifecycle events (`@Observes StartupEvent/ShutdownEvent`)\n  - Removed manual `ExecutorService` and `Runnable` implementation\n  - Replaced with Spring's declarative `@JmsListener` annotation\n  - Converted to `@Component`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 10. **HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java`\n- **Changes**: Same as CargoHandledConsumer - replaced lifecycle with `@JmsListener`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 11. **DeliveredCargoConsumer.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/DeliveredCargoConsumer.java`\n- **Changes**: Same as CargoHandledConsumer - replaced lifecycle with `@JmsListener`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 12. **MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java`\n- **Changes**: Same as CargoHandledConsumer - replaced lifecycle with `@JmsListener`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n### 13. **RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java**\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java`\n- **Changes**: Same as CargoHandledConsumer - replaced lifecycle with `@JmsListener`\n- **Status**: Successfully written\n\n## Key Migration Patterns Applied\n\n1. **Dependency Injection**: CDI (`@Inject`, `@ApplicationScoped`) → Spring (`@Autowired`, `@Service`, `@Repository`, `@Component`, `@Configuration`)\n2. **Configuration**: MicroProfile `@ConfigProperty` → Spring `@Value`\n3. **JPA**: Quarkus Panache → Standard JPA with `@PersistenceContext`\n4. **Transactions**: Jakarta `@Transactional` → Spring `@Transactional`\n5. **Events**: CDI `Event<T>` → Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n6. **REST Client**: JAX-RS `WebTarget` → Spring `RestTemplate`\n7. **JMS Producer**: Manual `JMSContext` → Spring `JmsTemplate`\n8. **JMS Consumer**: Quarkus lifecycle + manual threads → Spring `@JmsListener`\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated and are ready for use with Spring Boot!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6fabce19-5bc2-4de5-94d2-1fb45743d165","uuid":"0841b8be-ec8f-44a1-94ff-977daba35c02"}
