kus Panache `Sort` with Spring `Sort`\n\n#### 6. **File Processing Classes** (7 files)\n\n**EventFilesCheckpoint.java**\n- Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/EventFilesCheckpoint.java`\n- Changes: No changes needed (plain POJO)\n\n**EventItemReader.java**\n- Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/EventItemReader.java`\n- Changes: Removed `@Dependent`, `@Named`, JBatch `AbstractItemReader`, `JobContext`; changed to `@Component`, `@Autowired`, `@Value` for properties\n\n**EventItemWriter.java**\n- Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/EventItemWriter.java`\n- Changes: Removed `@Dependent`, `@Named`, JBatch `AbstractItemWriter`, `JobContext`; changed to `@Component`, `@Autowired`, `@Value`, `@Transactional`\n\n**EventLineParseException.java**\n- Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/EventLineParseException.java`\n- Changes: No changes needed (plain exception class)\n\n**FileProcessorJobListener.java**\n- Location: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/FileProcessorJobListener.java`\n- Changes: Removed `@Dependent`, `@Named`, JBatch `JobListener`; changed to `@Component`, `@Autowired`\n\n**LineParseExceptionListener.java**\n- Location: `/home/bmcginn/git