{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01XRaE8xsFftc7MjGDwVBcSz","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.eclipse.cargotracker.application.util;\n     2→\n     3→import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\n     4→import org.springframework.boot.context.event.ApplicationReadyEvent;\n     5→import org.springframework.context.event.EventListener;\n     6→import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n     7→\n     8→/** Loads sample data for demo. */\n     9→@Component\n    10→public class SampleDataGenerator {\n    11→\n    12→    @Autowired\n    13→    private InitLoader loader;\n    14→\n    15→    @EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class)\n    16→    public void loadSampleData() {\n    17→        loader.loadData();\n    18→    }\n    19→}\n    20→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6fabce19-5bc2-4de5-94d2-1fb45743d165","uuid":"105ca516-d93e-402c-a11a-ebcfe07d8fb1"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01YCNbvNZwgb8Py8ELf6sEYi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I understand the full flow. The `SampleDataGenerator` runs on `ApplicationReadyEvent` and calls `InitLoader.loadData()`, which checks `ApplicationSettings` row (id=1) to see if samples are loaded. The `import.sql` inserts that initial row.\n\nThe fix: remove the explicit `spring.sql.init` configuration and let Hibernate's built-in `import.sql` mechanism handle it. When `ddl-auto=create-drop`, Hibernate will automatically execute `import.sql` after schema creation."}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":422,"cache_read_input_tokens":40053,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":422,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":438},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6fabce19-5bc2-4de5-94d2-1fb45743d165","uuid":"995b2cae-0b4a-4002-9984-47132e62aff3"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01YCNbvNZwgb8Py8ELf6sEYi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01HhvD6QrV6adrqQ1BzEZ6hd","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/src/main/resources/application.properties","old_string":"# JPA / Hibernate\nspring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create-drop\nspring.jpa.show-sql=true\nspring.jpa.properties.hibernate.format_sql=false\nspring.jpa.defer-datasource-initialization=true\n\n# SQL initialization\nspring.sql.init.mode=always\nspring.sql.init.data-locations=classpath:import.sql","new_string":"# JPA / Hibernate\nspring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create-drop\nspring.jpa.show-sql=true\nspring.jpa.properties.hibernate.format_sql=false\n# Hibernate natively loads import.sql after schema creation when ddl-auto is set\nspring.sql.init.mode=never"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":422,"cache_read_input_tokens":40053,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":422,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":438},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6fabce19-5bc2-4de5-94d2-1fb45743d165","uuid":"ffb5c9a5-2aac-45ac-9180-d70c530ed431"}
