{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01GwCaNRY3pBafA5HfCFM7Ed","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Quarkus to Spring Boot migration is complete. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n**Migration Complete - All tasks finished successfully.**\n\n### Key Results:\n- **Docker image**: Builds successfully (~3.3GB)\n- **Application startup**: ~10 seconds\n- **Smoke tests**: 7/7 passing\n  - Health endpoint (UP)\n  - 13 locations listed\n  - 4 sample cargos loaded\n  - Cargo details retrieval (ABC123)\n  - 4 tracking IDs returned\n  - Graph traversal returns 3 route paths\n  - Handling event report submission works\n\n### Issues Fixed During Migration:\n1. **Missing dependencies**: Added `commons-lang3` and `jakarta.xml.bind-api` for domain model classes\n2. **`@Override` on non-interface method**: Removed from `JmsApplicationEvents.cargoWasRerouted`\n3. **Spring Data Sort reference**: Removed from `EventLogger` (custom repo doesn't support it)\n4. **import.sql table naming**: Changed `ApplicationSettings` to `application_settings` (Hibernate snake_case default)\n5. **SQL init ordering**: Switched from Spring SQL init to Hibernate's native `import.sql` mechanism\n6. **Actuator path**: Fixed smoke test to use context-path-prefixed actuator URL\n\n### Files Changed:\n- ~50+ Java files migrated from Quarkus annotations to Spring Boot\n- New: `CargoTrackerApplication.java`, `BookingRestController.java`, `smoke.py`, `CHANGELOG.md`\n- Removed: JSF templates, batch job XML, Quarkus-specific Dockerfiles, old tests"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":384,"cache_read_input_tokens":61691,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":384,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":394},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6fabce19-5bc2-4de5-94d2-1fb45743d165","uuid":"04c3d256-09a5-45fe-bb64-8385b6c7e1f1"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1973513,"duration_api_ms":2238165,"num_turns":124,"result":"The Quarkus to Spring Boot migration is complete. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n**Migration Complete - All tasks finished successfully.**\n\n### Key Results:\n- **Docker image**: Builds successfully (~3.3GB)\n- **Application startup**: ~10 seconds\n- **Smoke tests**: 7/7 passing\n  - Health endpoint (UP)\n  - 13 locations listed\n  - 4 sample cargos loaded\n  - Cargo details retrieval (ABC123)\n  - 4 tracking IDs returned\n  - Graph traversal returns 3 route paths\n  - Handling event report submission works\n\n### Issues Fixed During Migration:\n1. **Missing dependencies**: Added `commons-lang3` and `jakarta.xml.bind-api` for domain model classes\n2. **`@Override` on non-interface method**: Removed from `JmsApplicationEvents.cargoWasRerouted`\n3. **Spring Data Sort reference**: Removed from `EventLogger` (custom repo doesn't support it)\n4. **import.sql table naming**: Changed `ApplicationSettings` to `application_settings` (Hibernate snake_case default)\n5. **SQL init ordering**: Switched from Spring SQL init to Hibernate's native `import.sql` mechanism\n6. **Actuator path**: Fixed smoke test to use context-path-prefixed actuator URL\n\n### Files Changed:\n- ~50+ Java files migrated from Quarkus annotations to Spring Boot\n- New: `CargoTrackerApplication.java`, `BookingRestController.java`, `smoke.py`, `CHANGELOG.md`\n- Removed: JSF templates, batch job XML, Quarkus-specific Dockerfiles, old tests","session_id":"6fabce19-5bc2-4de5-94d2-1fb45743d165","total_cost_usd":28.31620577,"usage":{"input_tokens":88,"cache_creation_input_tokens":379194,"cache_read_input_tokens":6200716,"output_tokens":53446,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":379194}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":33